克勞蒂雅·安·克利斯丁（{{lang-en|Claudia Ann Christian}}<ref name=birth>{{Cite web |url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/63/Claudia-Christian.html |title=Claudia Christian Biography (1965–)<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2020-08-01 |archive-date=2018-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180810112142/http://www.filmreference.com/film/63/Claudia-Christian.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，原父姓'''Coghlan'''<ref>According to the State of California. ''California Birth Index, 1905–1995''. Center for Health Statistics, California Department of Health Services, Sacramento, California. Searchable at http://www.familytreelegends.com/records/39461. {{subscription}} {{Wayback|url=http://www.familytreelegends.com/records/39461 |date=20140906084832 }}</ref>，{{bd|1965年|8月10日}}）<ref name=birth />是一名美國演員和歌手，最廣為人知的是他在科幻影集《[[巴比倫五號|巴比倫五號]]》的演出。他也曾在[[貝塞斯達軟體|貝塞斯達軟體]]的電玩遊戲[[上古卷軸V：無界天際|上古卷軸V：無界天際]]和[[異塵餘生4|異塵餘生4]]中配音<ref name=ClaudiaChristianTVCom>{{cite web|url=http://www.tv.com/claudia-christian/person/22140/summary.html|title=Claudia Christian|website=[[TV.com|TV.com]]|access-date=June 19, 2012|date=|archive-date=2011-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110407105926/http://www.tv.com/claudia-christian/person/22140/summary.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.mahalo.com/claudia-christian Claudia Christian]. Mahalo.com. Retrieved on 2012-06-19. {{Wayback|url=http://www.mahalo.com/claudia-christian |date=20101123195248 }}</ref><ref>[http://pizza-morgana.com/about/cast About The Cast] {{Wayback|url=http://pizza-morgana.com/about/cast |date=20160303175907 }}. Pizza Morgana. Retrieved on 2012-06-19.</ref>。他致力於推廣辛克萊療法，即使用[[納曲酮|納曲酮]]（Naltrexone）來治療[[酒精成癮|酒精成癮]]<ref name=C3Found/>。

==早年生活==
克勞蒂雅·克利斯丁出生於加州[[格倫代爾_(加利福尼亞州)|格倫代爾]]，來自德國的母親 Hildegard（原姓克利斯丁）是時裝業的主管，父親 James Michael Coghlan 有愛爾蘭血統<ref>[https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/access/61285177.html?dids=61285177:61285177&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=May+10%2C+1991&author=ROSE-MARIE+TURK&pub=Los+Angeles+Times+(pre-1997+Fulltext)&desc=Give+and+Take+Mothers+in+the+Business+of+Dressing+Well+Swap+Clothes+With+Their+Grateful+Daughters&pqatl=google Los Angeles Times: Archives – Give and Take Mothers in the Business of Dressing Well Swap Clothes With Their Grateful Daughters<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://articles.latimes.com/1991-05-10/news/vw-1444_1_cocktail-dress |title=Give and Take : Mothers in the Business of Dressing Well Swap Clothes With Their Grateful Daughters – Los Angeles Times<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2020-08-01 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306134535/http://articles.latimes.com/1991-05-10/news/vw-1444_1_cocktail-dress |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Now+I've+found+my+own+space%3B+Babylon+5+'s+Claudia+on+the+split+from...-a077308608 |title=Now I've found my own space; Babylon 5 's Claudia on the split from Scots Braveheart Angus MacFadyen. – Free Online Library<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2020-08-01 |archive-date=2020-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731223918/https://www.thefreelibrary.com/Now+I've+found+my+own+space%3B+Babylon+5+'s+Claudia+on+the+split+from...-a077308608 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=clagl>{{Cite web |url=http://www.retrocrush.com/archive2007/claudia/ |title=retroCRUSH: The World's Greatest Pop Culture Site<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=July 3, 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120504182501/http://www.retrocrush.com/archive2007/claudia/ |archive-date=2012-05-04 |url-status=dead |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/person/claudia-christian?filter-options=movies |title=Claudia Christian Profile – Metacritic<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2020-08-01 |archive-date=2017-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171028042425/http://www.metacritic.com/person/claudia-christian?filter-options=movies |dead-url=no }}</ref>。克利斯丁成長於美國[[康乃迪克州|康乃迪克州]]和英國<ref name=clagl/> 。

==事業==
克利斯丁最早於1984年開始出現在《T. J. Hooker》和《Dallas》等電視劇中<ref name=ClaudiaChristianTVCom /><ref>{{cite web|title=Actress Claudia Christian|series=AM Northwest|url=https://katu.com/amnw/actress-claudia-christian|website=KATU|date=June 3, 2014|access-date=November 7, 2018|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728150658/https://katu.com/amnw/actress-claudia-christian|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在1987年的電影《[[異形附身|異形附身]]》中也飾演一角<ref name=ClaudiaChristianTVCom />。

在1994～1998年間，克利斯丁在《巴比倫五號》飾演主要角色。在第五季他並未續約出演，具體的原因他和節目製作人[[約瑟夫·麥可·斯特拉日恩斯基|斯特拉日恩斯基]]各執一詞<ref>''Christian, Claudia, Buchanan, Morgan Grant.'' Chapter 8. Death by irony // Babylon Confidential: A Memoir of Love, Sex, and Addiction. BenBella Books, 2012. P. [https://books.google.com.ua/books?id=FD66iGEZ2zIC&pg=PA146 132–134] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com.ua/books?id=FD66iGEZ2zIC&pg=PA146 |date=20200728150254 }}. {{ISBN|978-1-93785606-9}}.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.midwinter.com/lurk/misc/cc-leave.html|title=About Claudia Christian's Departure|work=The Lurker's Guide to Babylon 5|author=Joe M. Straczynski, Claudia Christian (quoted from correspondence)|accessdate=2020-08-01|archive-date=2006-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061019022537/http://www.midwinter.com/lurk/misc/cc-leave.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。之後他有回到該劇集的電視電視中出演。

克利斯丁出過四張唱片：1996 年和演員Claudia Cummings合作的《Claudia Squared》、1998 年的單曲《Taboo》以及和其他巴比倫五號演員合作的《The Be Five》、和 2001 年的個人專輯《Once Upon a Time》<ref name=ClaudiaChristianTVCom />。

1999年他在《[[花花公子|花花公子]]》中登出裸照。2000年後他偶爾出現在一些美國和英國的一些電視劇、舞臺劇和廣播劇中出現。克利斯丁最近的活動是 2014 年在[[星海爭霸II：虛空之遺|星海爭霸II：虛空之遺]]替[[神族_(星海爭霸)|神族]]角色洛哈娜配音、2016 年在遊戲[[決勝時刻：無盡戰爭|決勝時刻：無盡戰爭]]中飾演費蘭艦長（Captain Ferran），以及在未上映的 Netflix 動畫《Gods and Heroes》中配音。

==公益==
克利斯丁曾經長期受酒癮困擾，據他的說法曾瀕臨死亡，後來發現辛克萊療法才成功治好。之後他希望能幫助其他有類似困難的人，致力於推廣此療法，曾為此演講、著書、拍攝紀錄片<ref name=Description_of_cure> {{cite book |author3=Dr. Roy Eskapa |author2=Morgan Grant Buchanan |author1=Claudia Christian |title=Babylon Confidential |url=https://archive.org/details/babylonconfident0000chri |date=2012 |publisher=BenBella Books, Inc. |isbn=978-1-937856-06-9 |pages=Afterword |edition=First}}</ref><ref name=C3_website>{{cite web |title=C3 Foundation website |url=http://www.cthreefoundation.org |publisher=C Three Foundation |accessdate=December 22, 2013 |archive-date=2020-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731232032/https://cthreefoundation.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Atlantic">{{cite news|last1=Glaser|first1=Gabrielle|title=The Irrationality of Alcoholics Anonymous|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2015/04/the-irrationality-of-alcoholics-anonymous/386255/|accessdate=24 September 2017|publisher=The Atlantic|date=April 2015|archive-date=2019-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190528155712/https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2015/04/the-irrationality-of-alcoholics-anonymous/386255/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=OLP>{{cite web |title=One Little Pill |url=http://www.cthreefoundation.org/one-little-pill.html |accessdate=September 10, 2013 |archive-date=2017-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924185129/http://www.cthreefoundation.org/one-little-pill.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=C3Found>{{cite web |title=C3 Foundation |url=http://cthreefoundation.org |accessdate=July 22, 2013 |archive-date=2013-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130803130055/http://www.cthreefoundation.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

